import Projects from "./pages/Projects"
import Experience from "./pages/Experience"
import About from "./pages/About"

import { 
  BrowserRouter as Router, 
  Route, 
  Switch, 
  Link, 
  Redirect 
} from "react-router-dom"

{/* <Aboutme
content="I’m currently interested in product & project managment, blockchain, DevOps, and UX design. 
You can catch me doing Hackathons, personal projects, LeetCode, and applying to (lots of) jobs!"
/> */}

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path="/">
          <Projects />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path="/experience">
          <Experience />
        </Route>
        <Route exact path="/about">
          <About />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
